**Important points**:

 1. I recommend you use [`LocalDate#minusMonths`](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/time/LocalDate.html#minusMonths-long-) i.e. instead of using `date.plusMonths(-1L * auditTimeMonthLimit)`, you should use `date.minusMonths(auditTimeMonthLimit)`.
